---
// signal-steering Übersicht: synthetische Daten → 3 Methoden (sie widersprechen
// sich) → ein belastbares Signal → Budget-Steuerung.
// Grün = selbst entwickelt · Grau = Marktlösungen & Rohdaten.
---

<div class="mts-wrap">
  <div class="mts">
    <!-- TOP: Daten → Budget-Steuerung (Lernschleife) -->
    <div class="mts-top">
      <div class="mts-box built">
        <div class="mts-box-t">Daten (synthetisch)</div>
        <div class="mts-box-s">PMax + Meta · BigQuery</div>
      </div>
      <div class="mts-conn" aria-hidden="true">→</div>
      <div class="mts-box built">
        <div class="mts-box-t">Budget-Steuerung</div>
        <div class="mts-box-s">lenkt den nächsten Euro</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- TRIANGULATION -->
    <div class="mts-panel">
      <div class="mts-panel-h">Drei Methoden messen dieselben Daten</div>
      <div class="mts-lenses">
        <div class="mts-lens built">
          <div class="ml-t">Plattform (Last-Click)</div>
          <div class="ml-s">schnell, überschätzt</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mts-lens built">
          <div class="ml-t">Geo-Experiment</div>
          <div class="ml-s">echter Lift, belastbar</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mts-lens built">
          <div class="ml-t">Mix-Modell (MMM)</div>
          <div class="ml-s">Langzeit-Wirkung</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ERGEBNIS der drei Methoden (kein gebautes Element) -->
    <div class="mts-down" aria-hidden="true">↓</div>
    <div class="mts-result">
      <span class="mts-result-tag">Ergebnis</span>
      <span class="mts-result-text">
        Sie widersprechen sich. Das belastbare Signal kommt aus Geo-Experiment +
        Modell.
      </span>
    </div>

    <!-- MARKT -->
    <div class="mts-market">
      <div class="mts-market-h">Marktlösungen decken je nur eine Methode</div>
      <div class="mts-market-grid">
        <div class="mts-mcard">
          <div class="mm-t">Plattform &amp; Bidding</div>
          <div class="mm-s">Smart Bidding · PMax<br />Meta · Skai · Marin</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mts-mcard">
          <div class="mm-t">Geo-Experimente</div>
          <div class="mm-s">GeoLift · Measured<br />Haus · INCRMNTAL</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mts-mcard">
          <div class="mm-t">MMM-Tools</div>
          <div class="mm-s">Meridian · Robyn<br />Recast · Mutinex</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mts-blended">
        Blended-SaaS (Northbeam, Triple Whale) mischt zwei Methoden, ist aber
        selbst Blackbox: kein Zugriff auf das eigene Steering.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mts-legend">
      <span class="lg-swatch lg-built" aria-hidden="true"></span> Grün = selbst
      entwickelt
      <span class="lg-sep" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="lg-swatch lg-grey" aria-hidden="true"></span> Grau =
      Marktlösungen &amp; Rohdaten
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .mts-wrap {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .mts {
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6),
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4)
    );
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-soft);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 1.4rem 1.5rem;
  }

  /* one build colour: green */
  .built {
    background: rgba(46, 139, 87, 0.16);
    border: 1px solid rgba(46, 139, 87, 0.55);
  }
  .built .mts-box-t,
  .built .ml-t {
    color: #1d6b3f;
  }

  /* ---- TOP flow ---- */
  .mts-top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: stretch;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
  }
  .mts-box {
    flex: 1;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 0.7rem 0.95rem;
    position: relative;
  }
